" The complexity of the current situation requires that military take a more direct role in securing southern border than in the recent past. "
The Roosevelt reservation covers California, New Mexico and Arizona and was designated as federal land by Theodore Roosevelt in 1907 to keep the border.
The memorandum added that the secretary of defense can" determine those military activities that are reasonably necessary and APPROpiate to accomplish the mission" of keeping the border secure.
